data.description: Large house and very large residential lot with plenty of room for all located in Refugio, Tx.   This house has a large open floor plan with the kitchen, dining and living room big enough for entertaining many comfortably. Are you also needing a home with lots of bedrooms? This is then the house for you.  This house consists of 5 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms with about 2040 square feet of living space.  There was some nice remodeling done in 2012 but is ready for you to add your own touches and repairs to make it a beautiful large home.  The split bedrooms flank each side of the house, and the primary bedroom is at the back. The house sits on almost half-an-acre lot!  There is so much room in the side and back yard and the lot has beautiful big trees. The roof was installed in December 2017.  Call soon and come take a look at this great value house and turn it into your Home!
